Tags : latest on earthquake in Sikkim , latest on foreign tourists stranded in Sikkim , news on Sikkim after earthquake , rescue operation in Sikkim 18 killed as powerful earthquake jolts northeast , Nepal 18 Sep 2011 A powerful earthquake with a 6 . 8 magnitude jolted Sikkim and several areas of northeast and neighbouring Nepal on Sunday leaving at least 18 persons dead and over 100 injured besides causing extensive damage to several buildings .